{"tid":2487365,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港新版小學課本刪「毒教材」，「中華民國遷台」改稱國民黨","createTime":"2021-04-13T13:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T16:33:27.000Z","uid":211994,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"773a9de93693ce30c6cbbd51156ee6a2844c5a0a","tid":2487365,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T13:15:44.000Z","msg":"想閱讀全文請click入去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下面有啲重點<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-textbook-04122021141508.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Fhk-textbook-04122021141508.html&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11P2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=a2b2fcb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-textbook-04122021141508.html</a><br />\n<br />\n...其中「內外交困的時期」一課交代國共內戰中，舊版稱「最後由毛澤東領導的中國共產黨取得勝利，並於1949年10月1日宣布成立中華人民共和國；由蔣介石領導的中華民國政府則遷至台灣」<br />\n<br />\n；至於新版，出版社網站去年10月表明，上述段落尾句將改為「由蔣介石領導的中國國民黨則遷至台灣」；同一課其他頁數亦見類似修訂..."},{"pid":"928a3d954340f1d35f40382d01e372cc5ea954e4","tid":2487365,"uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T13:17:12.000Z","msg":"...此外，有高中中史課本，亦對有關中日二戰及五四運動的章節作出修訂，涉及五四運動的3條課堂討論全部換走，拿走討論代入當時學生面對政治上不公義，會否採取激進手段以示不滿<br />\n<br />\n；北洋政府派軍警鎮壓及逮捕學生是否合理；對警民衝突兩方表現的意見..."},{"pid":"aa4fc8da7721b5f36048e8fe6e590d74c2108771","tid":2487365,"uid":211994,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T13:18:10.000Z","msg":"香港人應建立自己嘅線上歷史資料庫。<br />\n可能已經有？如果有麻煩直接回覆呢條留言，我幫你pin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4879d9aea16822aefae1f57f31a2d42f6b374e80","tid":2487365,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d422b42f605b407f51843d073eb36ecf6ab62f1","tid":2487365,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/